  "title": "CHEF",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare and cook a variety of dishes according to recipes and standards</p></li><li><p>Maintain high food quality, hygiene, and presentation</p></li><li><p>Plan menus and manage kitchen inventory</p></li><li><p>Supervise kitchen staff and ensure smooth daily operations</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and safety in the kitchen at all times</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a Chef or Cook</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of various cuisines and cooking techniques</p></li><li><p>Good leadership and communication skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work under pressure and during peak hours</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude and strong team spirit</p></li></ul>",
